(188, 3, 'Mat for sauna 50*150 cm', '', '<p>One of the most important accessories for steam room is a bathroom Mat that protects bare parts of the human body from the hot surfaces.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe spectacular design of the bath Mat in the style of a traditional craft is made from one hundred percent cotton. He will transform bath interior, adding warmth and identity.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe rug does not cause allergies, because of its naturalness, and extremely pleasant to the touch.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe fabric dries quickly, absorbs moisture easily and keeps the visual appeal after many washings. Weave in the fabric perfectly hinders small dust particles and debris, not allowing them to spread in the room.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMat &nbsp;sauna 50*150 cm large &nbsp;B/W</p>\r\n', '', '', ''),
(189, 1, 'Традиционное турецкое полотенце \"Пештемаль\"', '', '<p>Полотенце &laquo;Пештемаль&raquo; - &nbsp;турецкое &ndash; хлопковое изделие для саун и парных. Оно великолепно пропитывает влагу, а кожа дышит. Его можно использовать как килт для мужчин, и как парео для женщин.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '', ''),
(189, 2, 'Дәстүрлі түрік орамал \"Пештемаль\"', '', '<p>Сүлгі &laquo;Пештемаль&raquo; - &nbsp;түрік &laquo; мақта бұйым үшін сауналар және жұптық. Ол тамаша пропитывает ылғалды, тегіс, тыныстап. Оның пайдалануға болады килт ерлер үшін, парео әйелдер үшін.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '', ''),
(189, 3, 'Traditional Turkish towel \"Pestemal\"', '', '<p>Towel &laquo;Peshtemal&rdquo; - &nbsp;Turkish &ndash; cotton, the product for saunas and steam rooms. It perfectly nourishes the moisture, and the skin breathes. It can be used as a kilt for men, and as shawls for women.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '', ''),
