(657, 3, 'Steam Generator \"Parafon - 2\"', '', '<p>Is a special device that generates from water in the jet gazopa-modern flow chimney water vapor with a temperature of 500 degrees Celsius. The use of parafon allows to obtain a favourable steam background inside a Mobile bath, to increase comfort bath treatment, hard to block infrared radiation from the hot metal surfaces of the furnace and flue. More economically consumed the wood.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;In form it is cylindrical tank made of heat-resistant steel sheet AISI 430 thickness-tion of 0.5 mm, using the adapter built into the flue pipe diameter of 90 mm. work item Parafon &ndash; built-in steam generator made of stainless steel AISI - 430. Outside Parafon - 2-protected convertible heater that prevents the possibility of sunburn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;At the top of Parapona - 2 fuel filler neck, which is filled with up to 2.5 litres of water. After lighting the oven, Paragon goes into operation mode after 15 minutes. The output is a dry high-energy superheated steam, which is fed to a special bumper-diffuser at the bottom of Parafon. The steam generator has a metal handle for easy carrying.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Packed in a transport bag and carton.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '', ''),
