(824, 3, 'Timber 45 x 50 mm', '', '<p>In recent years, increasingly gaining momentum building material timber is calibrated. This product is produced from the integral of the logs, which are subjected to a special sawing and processing. The visual side can be rounded or straight. One of its sides planed and the other two have the grooves and spikes.<br />\r\nPlaned timber (calibrated) has advantages:<br />\r\nBrilliant heat insulation<br />\r\nVisual appeal<br />\r\nNatural<br />\r\nStrength<br />\r\nLong-term<br />\r\nFor its production we use pine, beech, birch, ash, cedar, spruce and aspen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Price per meter.</p>\r\n', '', '', ''),
