(1438, 3, 'Timber 50*50*2', '', 'In recent years more and more gaining momentum building material timber is planed. This product is produced from the integral of the logs, which are subjected to a special sawing and processing.<br />\r\nThe visual side can be rounded or straight. One of its sides planed and the other two have spikes and grooves.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlaned timber (calibrated) has advantages:<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBrilliant heat insulation<br />\r\n<br />\r\nVisual appeal<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNatural<br />\r\n<br />\r\nStrength<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLong-term<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFor its production we use pine, beech, birch, ash, cedar, spruce and aspen.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPrice per meter.<br />\r\n&nbsp;', '', '', ''),
