(1466, 3, 'Oven \"Ermak - 20\" Premium (2017) - Stainless Steel.steel', '', 'This is a modular compact stove for baths which has excellent quality and different replacement options. The use of options and hidden heater will allow you to create the right climate in the bathhouse (Hammam, Russian bath, Finnish sauna). Water and air are heated rapidly, and in the neighboring areas.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe amount of steam: 8 to 18 m3.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGeneral information:<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe arch of the furnace of steel: 8 mm<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFast&nbsp;heat rooms<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nLarge firebox&nbsp;&nbsp;with a length of log&nbsp;up to 550 mm<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nHigh efficiency&nbsp;and quality of use<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nThe use of&nbsp;closed heater&nbsp;and receiving a fine couple<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nReversible&nbsp;fire door<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nSmokerdata&nbsp;handle<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nIn the model of the furnace &laquo;Ermak &ndash; 20\" premium (stainless.St.) used the heater, and the furnace of steel, hardened in places of the greatest heat loads of up to 8 mm.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDoor, metal, reversible inscribed in a frame of stainless steel. The product is dominated by classic black matte finish, excellent ergonomics that allows you to save space in the steam room.<br />\r\n&nbsp;', '', '', ''),
